    <item>
      <title>Planted clique problem</title>
      <link>https://simonvary.com/notes/planted-clique-problem/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Nov 2021 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://simonvary.com/notes/planted-clique-problem/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;The following is very difficult to solve&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;$$ \max_{x} \lVert A x \rVert_2, \quad \mathrm{s.t.} \quad \lVert x\rVert_0 \leq s, \lVert x\rVert_2 = 1, $$&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;when $s = \mathcal{O}(\log(n))$ and reasonably difficult when $s = \mathcal{O}(\sqrt{n})$&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;definition&#34;&gt;Definition&lt;/h3&gt;</description>
    </item>
