    <item>
      <title>Research</title>
      <link>https://simonvary.com/research/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://simonvary.com/research/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;My research focuses on optimization, statistical learning theory, and large language models:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Stability and generalization&lt;/strong&gt; of stochastic algorithms&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Stochastic and preconditioned optimization&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Riemannian and low-rank optimization&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Data attribution, interpretability, and efficient inference&lt;/strong&gt; for LLMs&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;For a complete and up-to-date citation list, see my &lt;a href=&#34;https://scholar.google.com/citations?user=V6OqU-cAAAAJ&amp;amp;hl=en&#34;&gt;Google Scholar profile&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;preprints&#34;&gt;Preprints&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;publication&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;publication-title&#34;&gt;A Nesterov-style Accelerated Gradient Descent Algorithm for the Symmetric Eigenvalue Problem&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;publication-authors&#34;&gt;F. Alimisis, S. Vary, B. Vandereycken&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;publication-meta&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;publication-venue&#34;&gt;Preprint, 2024&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;publication-links&#34;&gt; · [&lt;a href=&#34;https://arxiv.org/abs/2406.18433&#34;&gt;arXiv&lt;/a&gt;] &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;selected-publications&#34;&gt;Selected publications&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;publication&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;publication-title&#34;&gt;On-Average Stability of Multipass Preconditioned SGD and Effective Dimension&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;publication-authors&#34;&gt;S. Vary, T. Farghly, I. Kuzborskij, P. Rebeschini&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;publication-meta&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;publication-venue&#34;&gt;COLT, accepted, 2026&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;publication-links&#34;&gt; · [&lt;a href=&#34;https://arxiv.org/abs/2603.11989&#34;&gt;arXiv&lt;/a&gt;] &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;publication&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;publication-title&#34;&gt;Does Stochastic Gradient really succeed for Bandits?&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;publication-authors&#34;&gt;D. Baudry, E. Johnson, S. Vary, C. Pike-Burke, P. Rebeschini&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;publication-meta&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;publication-venue&#34;&gt;NeurIPS, oral, 2025&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;publication-links&#34;&gt; · [&lt;a href=&#34;https://openreview.net/forum?id=gL4muAFwsh&#34;&gt;Proceedings&lt;/a&gt;] &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;publication&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;publication-title&#34;&gt;Black-Box Uniform Stability for Non-Euclidean Empirical Risk Minimization&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;publication-authors&#34;&gt;S. Vary, D. Martínez-Rubio, P. Rebeschini&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;publication-meta&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;publication-venue&#34;&gt;AISTATS, 2025&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;publication-links&#34;&gt; · [&lt;a href=&#34;https://arxiv.org/abs/2412.15956&#34;&gt;arXiv&lt;/a&gt;] &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;publication&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;publication-title&#34;&gt;Optimization without retraction on the random generalized Stiefel manifold&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;publication-authors&#34;&gt;S. Vary, P. Ablin, B. Gao, P.-A. Absil&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;publication-meta&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;publication-venue&#34;&gt;ICML, 2024&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;publication-links&#34;&gt; · [&lt;a href=&#34;https://simonvary.com/papers/Vary2024Landing.pdf&#34;&gt;PDF&lt;/a&gt;] [&lt;a href=&#34;https://proceedings.mlr.press/v235/vary24a.html&#34;&gt;Proceedings&lt;/a&gt;] [&lt;a href=&#34;https://arxiv.org/abs/2405.01702&#34;&gt;arXiv&lt;/a&gt;] [&lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/simonvary/landing-generalized-stiefel&#34;&gt;Code&lt;/a&gt;] &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;publication&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;publication-title&#34;&gt;Compressed sensing of low-rank plus sparse matrices&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;publication-authors&#34;&gt;J. Tanner, S. Vary&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;publication-meta&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;publication-venue&#34;&gt;Applied and Computational Harmonic Analysis, 64, 254–293, 2023&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;publication-links&#34;&gt; · [&lt;a href=&#34;https://simonvary.com/papers/TaVa_lrps.pdf&#34;&gt;PDF&lt;/a&gt;] [&lt;a href=&#34;https://doi.org/10.1016/j.acha.2023.01.008&#34;&gt;DOI&lt;/a&gt;] [&lt;a href=&#34;https://arxiv.org/abs/2007.09457&#34;&gt;arXiv&lt;/a&gt;] &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;publications&#34;&gt;Publications&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;publication&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;publication-title&#34;&gt;Infeasible Deterministic, Stochastic, and Variance-Reduction Algorithms for Optimization under Orthogonality Constraints&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;publication-authors&#34;&gt;P. Ablin, S. Vary, B. Gao, P.-A. Absil&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;publication-meta&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;publication-venue&#34;&gt;JMLR, 2024&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;publication-links&#34;&gt; · [&lt;a href=&#34;https://arxiv.org/abs/2303.16510&#34;&gt;arXiv&lt;/a&gt;] [&lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/simonvary/landing-stiefel&#34;&gt;Code&lt;/a&gt;] &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;publication&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;publication-title&#34;&gt;An Alternating Minimization Algorithm with Trajectory for Direct Exoplanet Detection — The AMAT Algorithm&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;publication-authors&#34;&gt;H. Daglayan, S. Vary, O. Absil, F. Cantalloube, V. Christiaens, N. Gillis, L. Jacques, V. Leplat, P.-A. Absil&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;publication-meta&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;publication-venue&#34;&gt;Astronomy &amp;amp; Astrophysics, 692 (A126), 2024&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;publication-links&#34;&gt; · [&lt;a href=&#34;https://doi.org/10.1051/0004-6361/202451242&#34;&gt;DOI&lt;/a&gt;] [&lt;a href=&#34;https://arxiv.org/abs/2410.06310&#34;&gt;arXiv&lt;/a&gt;] &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;publication&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;publication-title&#34;&gt;A Riemannian Proximal Newton Method&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;publication-authors&#34;&gt;W. Si, P.-A. Absil, W. Huang, R. Jiang, S. Vary&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;publication-meta&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;publication-venue&#34;&gt;SIAM Journal on Optimization, 34(1), 654–681, 2024&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;publication-links&#34;&gt; · [&lt;a href=&#34;https://doi.org/10.1137/23M1565097&#34;&gt;DOI&lt;/a&gt;] [&lt;a href=&#34;https://arxiv.org/abs/2304.04032&#34;&gt;arXiv&lt;/a&gt;] &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;publication&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;publication-title&#34;&gt;Direct Exoplanet Detection Using L1 Norm Low-Rank Approximation&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;publication-authors&#34;&gt;H. Daglayan, S. Vary, V. Laplat, N. Gillis, P.-A. Absil&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;publication-meta&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;publication-venue&#34;&gt;Preprint, 2023&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;publication-links&#34;&gt; · [&lt;a href=&#34;https://arxiv.org/abs/2304.03619&#34;&gt;arXiv&lt;/a&gt;] &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;publication&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;publication-title&#34;&gt;Low-rank plus sparse trajectory decomposition for direct exoplanet imaging&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;publication-authors&#34;&gt;S. Vary, H. Daglayan, L. Jacques, P.-A. Absil&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;publication-meta&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;publication-venue&#34;&gt;IEEE (ICASSP) International Conference on Acoustics, Speech, and Signal Processing, 2023&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;publication-links&#34;&gt; · [&lt;a href=&#34;https://arxiv.org/abs/2301.07018&#34;&gt;arXiv&lt;/a&gt;] &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;publication&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;publication-title&#34;&gt;Likelihood ratio map for direct exoplanet detection&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;publication-authors&#34;&gt;H. Daglayan, S. Vary, F. Cantalloube, P.-A. Absil, O. Absil&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;publication-meta&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;publication-venue&#34;&gt;IEEE (IPAS) International Image Processing Applications and Systems, 2022&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;publication-links&#34;&gt; · [&lt;a href=&#34;https://arxiv.org/abs/2210.10609&#34;&gt;arXiv&lt;/a&gt;] &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;publication&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;publication-title&#34;&gt;Optimization flows landing on the Stiefel manifold&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;publication-authors&#34;&gt;B. Gao, S. Vary, P. Ablin, P.-A. Absil&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;publication-meta&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;publication-venue&#34;&gt;Proc. MTNS (IFAC-PapersOnLine) 55(30), 25–30, 2022&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;publication-links&#34;&gt; · [&lt;a href=&#34;https://doi.org/10.1016/j.ifacol.2022.11.023&#34;&gt;DOI&lt;/a&gt;] [&lt;a href=&#34;https://arxiv.org/abs/2202.09058&#34;&gt;arXiv&lt;/a&gt;] &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;publication&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;publication-title&#34;&gt;Matrix rigidity and the ill-posedness of Robust PCA and matrix completion&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;publication-authors&#34;&gt;J. Tanner, A. Thompson, S. Vary&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;publication-meta&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;publication-venue&#34;&gt;SIAM Journal on Mathematics of Data Science, 1(3), 537–554, 2019&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;publication-links&#34;&gt; · [&lt;a href=&#34;https://doi.org/10.1137/18M1227846&#34;&gt;DOI&lt;/a&gt;] [&lt;a href=&#34;https://arxiv.org/abs/1811.05919&#34;&gt;arXiv&lt;/a&gt;] &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;publication&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;publication-title&#34;&gt;Multispectral snapshot demosaicing via non-convex matrix completion&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;publication-authors&#34;&gt;G. A. Antonucci, S. Vary, D. Humphreys, R. A. Lamb, J. Piper, J. Tanner&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;publication-meta&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;publication-venue&#34;&gt;IEEE Data Science Workshop, 2019&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;publication-links&#34;&gt; · [&lt;a href=&#34;https://doi.org/10.1109/DSW.2019.8755561&#34;&gt;DOI&lt;/a&gt;] [&lt;a href=&#34;https://arxiv.org/abs/1902.11032&#34;&gt;arXiv&lt;/a&gt;] &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;publication&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;publication-title&#34;&gt;A computational approach to hyperspectral imaging for long-range target identification&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;publication-authors&#34;&gt;S. Vary, A. Thompson, D. Humphreys, J. Tanner, R. A. Lamb&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;publication-meta&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;publication-venue&#34;&gt;Proc. SPIE 10644, Algorithms and Technologies for Multispectral, Hyperspectral, and Ultraspectral Imagery (XXIV), 2018&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;publication-links&#34;&gt; · [&lt;a href=&#34;https://doi.org/10.1117/12.2305306&#34;&gt;DOI&lt;/a&gt;] &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;publication&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;publication-title&#34;&gt;Differentially expressed microRNAs in lung adenocarcinoma invert effects of copy number aberrations of prognostic genes&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;publication-authors&#34;&gt;T. Tokar, C. Pastrello, V. R. Ramnarine, C. Zhu, K.J. Craddock, L. A. Pikor, E. A. Vucic, S. Vary, F. A. Shepherd, M. Tsao, W. L. Lam, I. Jurisica&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;publication-meta&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;publication-venue&#34;&gt;Oncotarget, 2018&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;publication-links&#34;&gt; · [&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC5823624/&#34;&gt;Article&lt;/a&gt;] &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;thesis&#34;&gt;Thesis&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;publication&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;publication-title&#34;&gt;On low-rank plus sparse matrix sensing&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;publication-authors&#34;&gt;S. Vary&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;publication-meta&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;publication-venue&#34;&gt;DPhil dissertation, 2021&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;publication-links&#34;&gt; · [&lt;a href=&#34;https://simonvary.com/thesis.pdf&#34;&gt;PDF&lt;/a&gt;] &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
